@Node CRUS2 "Crusade > The Long Road [#2]"

 @{b}The Long Road [#2]@{ub} (1998)
 
 Earthforces mining operation on Regula 4 is threatening to destroy the rural
 colony. With the help of a rogue technomage, called Alwyn, they have managed
 to delay the operation by using pyrotechnics and frightening manifestations.
 But then a group of settlers decide to take the fight to Earthforce, and when
 Gideon and Galen arrive, matters are starting to take a turn for the worse.
 
