 @{b}Patterns Of The Soul [#5]@{ub} (1998)
 
 The crew of the Excalibur must locate a group of humans, that left the Earth
 during the time of the Drakh battle, to make sure that they are not infected
 with the plague. If they are infected, they could be infecting every one they
 meet along their way. The Excalibur tracks them down to a planet, Theta 49,
