@Node CRUS7 "Crusade > The Rules Of The Game [#7]"

 @{b}The Rules Of The Game [#7]@{ub} (1999)
 
 Gideon arrives on Babylon 5 to negotiate for the rights to land on the Lorkan
 homeworld. But the Lorkan's consider themselves morally superior to their
 galactic neighbours and see humans as an unwanted taint in the perfect picture
 they themselves present. When Gideon's determination persists, a pair of
 devout Lorkans seek a more permanent end to the debates.
 
 Meanwhile, Max Eilerson's ex-wife Cynthia Allen shows up with a request for
 help. She has borrowed money from the wrong people and now it's up to Eilerson
 to fix things his own way.
 
