 @{b}Appearances And Other Deceits [#8]@{ub} (1999)
 
 While visiting officers determine a new look for the Excalibur and its crew in
 order to improve morale back home, the Excalibur comes across a derelict alien
 spaceship where the crew have apparently killed each other, leaving just one
 survivor. When this survivor is revived, an alien lifeforce is released and
 takes possession of Janey's body, and with her help it then spreads, by touch,
