@Node CRUS13 "Crusade > Each Night I Dream Of Home [#13]"

 @{b}Each Night I Dream Of Home [#13]@{ub} (1998)
 
 Senator Redway boards the Excalibur and orders Gideon to return to Earth on a
 high priority mission. When they arrive, a lifepod is picked up. The occupant
 of the lifepod, Dr. Stephen Franklin, has agreed to infect a volunteer with
 the Drakh plague, hoping that it will give them a clue as to how it works. But
 before the tests can be completed, the Drakh detect them and attack.
 
